Name: Sex with Teachers
About the game: Sex with Teachers - is the simplest puzzle which can help you to develop your visual memory and enjoy hot pictures of sexy ladies. The idea of the game is easy - you need to find all pair cards on the every level. As soon as you do that, a large picture of one of the hot lady will be opened for you. After the doing all the twenty levels, a gallery will be opened and you can see all the girls more detailed. Play and have fun! KEY FEATURES: - Simple and clear gameplay. - Relaxing soundtrack. - Nice pictures. - An unforgettable experience.
